<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.6.2">
<l>piṇiyaviḻu naṟunīla malarkkiḻiyap peṭaiyōṭum</l>
<l>aṇimalarmēl matunukaru maṟukāla ciṟuvaṇṭē</l>
<l>maṇikaḻunīr maruṅkalarum vayalāli maṇavāḷaṉ</l>
<l>paṇiyaṟiyēṉ nīceṉṟeṉ payalainō yuraiyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Little six-legged bee who sucks the nectar on beautiful blossoms</l>
<l rend="indent">with [your] mate,</l>
<l>As [you] scratch at the fragrant blue lotus with buds opening,</l>
<l>I do not understand the actions of the bridegroom of Āli with paddy fields</l>
<l>Where on [all] sides jewel[-like] lilies flourish. Going [to him],</l>
<l rend="indent">speak of my sallowing illness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
